\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104leg1665703135358.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/leg1665703135358.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/leg1665703135358.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"leg1665703135358\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"leg1665703135358__unifend_406157\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Shut down or suspend the Uniface environment started by the deprecated\n         <code class=\"ph codeph\">unifbeg</code> function.</p>\n<div class=\"note important note_important\" id=\"leg1665703135358__note_N10023_N1001A_N10001\"><span class=\"note__title\">Important:</span> The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">unifend</span> function\n         is deprecated and should not be used. Instead, use the Call-In API, a collection of call-in\n         functions related to the ProcScript <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">activate</span> command. For more\n         information, see the \"Call-In Using the Call-In API\" topic.</div>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"leg1665703135358__topic_d122291e1_d122292e1_d122293e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"leg1665703135358__codeblock_agq_cc2_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">int unifend (level);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"leg1665703135358__topic_d86602e1_d86603e1_d86604e1_d86605e1_d86606e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d257963e73\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"leg1665703135358__parml_iwf_2c2_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">level</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Number specifying whether Uniface should be shut down or suspended.</dd>\n</dl>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"leg1665703135358__table_d14921e1_d14922e1_d14923e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Level for unifend</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"leg1665703135358__table_d14921e1_d14922e1_d14923e1__entry__1\">Value of Level</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"leg1665703135358__table_d14921e1_d14922e1_d14923e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"leg1665703135358__table_d14921e1_d14922e1_d14923e1__entry__1\">-1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"leg1665703135358__table_d14921e1_d14922e1_d14923e1__entry__2\">Shut down Uniface and terminate the\n                        program.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"leg1665703135358__table_d14921e1_d14922e1_d14923e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"leg1665703135358__table_d14921e1_d14922e1_d14923e1__entry__2\">Return control of keyboard to the 3GL\n                        application.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"leg1665703135358__table_d14921e1_d14922e1_d14923e1__entry__1\">1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"leg1665703135358__table_d14921e1_d14922e1_d14923e1__entry__2\">Clear screen and return control of keyboard and\n                        screen to the 3GL application.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"leg1665703135358__topic_d86607e1_d86608e1_d86609e1_d86610e1_d86611e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d257963e147\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"leg1665703135358__table_d14924e1_d14925e1_d14926e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by unifend</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"leg1665703135358__table_d14924e1_d14925e1_d14926e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"leg1665703135358__table_d14924e1_d14925e1_d14926e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"leg1665703135358__table_d14924e1_d14925e1_d14926e1__entry__1\">1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"leg1665703135358__table_d14924e1_d14925e1_d14926e1__entry__2\">The Uniface environment was successfully shut\n                        down.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"leg1665703135358__topic_d86612e1_d86613e1_d86614e1_d86615e1_d86616e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d257963e191\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"leg1665703135358__d6217e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">ulib</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"leg1665703135358__topic_d86617e1_d86618e1_d86619e1_d86620e1_d86621e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d257963e203\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"leg1665703135358__p_d122315e1_d122316e1_d122317e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">unifend</code> can be called from a 3GL\n            call-in application to shut down or suspend the Uniface environment. If the\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">level</var> parameter is -1, <code class=\"ph codeph\">unifend</code> will shut down the\n            Uniface environment as well as terminate the program (so control is not passed back to\n            your application). If level is one, the screen is cleared and control of the keyboard\n            and screen is returned to the calling 3GL. Additionally, for a character-mode\n            application only, the *Busy* indicator will be turned off, and the cursor will be\n            positioned on the bottom line of the screen.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"leg1665703135358__p_d122318e1_d122319e1_d122320e1\">The Uniface environment must be reinitialized with\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">unifbeg</code> if Uniface service routines are required after a\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">unifend</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"leg1665703135358__section_q3j_3c2_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d257963e229\">Example:  unifbeg, unifend, and urun for simple call-in</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following C code performs a straight-forward call-in:</p>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104leg1665703135358_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"leg1665703135358__codeblock_eby_jc2_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\nvoid main (void)\n{\n/* Tell unifbeg to use myapp.aps/myapp.asn */\nusetparm(0, \"myapp.aps\", \"\");\nunifbeg(0); /* Start Uniface interactive environment */\nurun(\"FRM\", 0, 0, 0, 0); /* Run form FRM with default size/position */\nunifend(-1); /* Shut down the Uniface environment */\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pmb1665702596322.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Call-In Using the Call-In API</a><p>The Uniface 3GL Call-in API is a collection of call-in functions related to the ProcScript activate command.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529528\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529528\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "unifend Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Shut down or suspend the Uniface environment started by the deprecated unifbeg function. Important: The unifend function is deprecated and should not be used. Instead, use the Call-In API, a collection of call-in functions related to the ProcScript activate command. For more information, see the \"Call-In Using the Call-In API\" topic. int unifend (level); Copy Parameters level Number specifying whether Uniface should be shut down or suspended. Table 1. Level for unifend Value of Level Meaning -1 Shut down Uniface and terminate the program. 0 Return control of keyboard to the 3GL application. 1 Clear screen and return control of keyboard and screen to the 3GL application. Return Values Table 2. Values returned by unifend Value Meaning 1 The Uniface environment was successfully shut down. Use Library: ulib Description unifend can be called from a 3GL call-in application to shut down or suspend the Uniface environment. If the level parameter is -1, unifend will shut down the Uniface environment as well as terminate the program (so control is not passed back to your application). If level is one, the screen is cleared and control of the keyboard and screen is returned to the calling 3GL. Additionally, for a character-mode application only, the *Busy* indicator will be turned off, and the cursor will be positioned on the bottom line of the screen. The Uniface environment must be reinitialized with unifbeg if Uniface service routines are required after a unifend . Example: unifbeg, unifend, and urun for simple call-in The following C code performs a straight-forward call-in: Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> void main (void) { /* Tell unifbeg to use myapp.aps/myapp.asn */ usetparm(0, \"myapp.aps\", \"\"); unifbeg(0); /* Start Uniface interactive environment */ urun(\"FRM\", 0, 0, 0, 0); /* Run form FRM with default size/position */ unifend(-1); /* Shut down the Uniface environment */ } Copy Related Links Call-In Using the Call-In API The Uniface 3GL Call-in API is a collection of call-in functions related to the ProcScript activate command. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}